            "\n",
            "### II. Key Concepts\n",
            "\n",
            "The \"Bio Python\" course will systematically cover the following core concepts, structured to build foundational knowledge and progressively introduce advanced topics:\n",
            "\n",
            "A. **Python Fundamentals for Biological Data:**\n",
            "    *   Introduction to Python syntax, data types (strings, lists, dictionaries, tuples), and control structures (loops, conditionals).\n",
            "    *   Functions, modules, and object-oriented programming principles.\n",
